OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain will gradually spread eastwards
OL,7,Fovernight, turning heavier and more
OL,8,Fpersistent later in the night. A
OL,9,Fbreezy but mild night to come under
OL,10,Fthe blanket of cloud.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA wet morning with the rain
OL,13,Fheavy in places. The rain will slowly
OL,14,Fease from the west throughout the
OL,15,Fafternoon with some brighter spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping. Feeling cool for early
OL,17,FJune.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
